    "task_context": "Sprint 1: Implement basic webhook delivery. A single service that POSTs event payloads to subscriber URLs and records whether delivery succeeded or failed. Sprint 2 (retry logic, backoff, subscription suspension) is explicitly deferred — do NOT implement it, but leave reasonable extension points (e.g., DeliveryResult carries enough info for a future retry scheduler to act on).",
